<|startoftext|>Dish: greek style pizza dough
Directions: measure out 1 / 4 cup water for the dough
add your flour to the larger mixing bowl and knead for about 10 minutes until the dough just becomes smooth
put your hands along the board and flatten it
add 1 / 2 to 1 cup dough and roll as much in your palm as you would a round cookie and flatten with your hands
if you take your hands off the board , they can burn easily !
place the dough into a bowl and allow it to rest for about 25 min then punch it up !
if you use a cookie cutter , cut the dough into 16 equal pieces and roll each piece into a disk
then roll each disk into a ball & press together to ensure its not too flat ! i used a pizza peel in a dough cutter to make it easier to cut
let rest on counter until ready to use ! cut dough into 1 1 / 2 inch rounds and transfer to a lightly floured surface and roll each into a 12 circle
using a sharp knife , cut the rounds with a large knife , making sure you cut through the entire pizza dough'<|endoftext|>
